		/SX/cgpa.txt


-------------------
Remarks:

	X in 'SX' is replaced with 1 or 2 for corresponding semester
		eg: /S1/script.sh


	Results of S1 & S2 are seperated into 2 sub directories named S! & S@ respectively.


